short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Split a grid of images (like a 4-by-4) generated by diffusion models by Midjourney or Stable Diffusion into individual images.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use the MJ Grid Splitter to split your Midjourney Grid into single images.
one click to download and save them into your computer.
